# Vercel Environment Variables - Ready to Import
# =====================================================
# 
# THIS IS THE MOST IMPORTANT STEP FOR TOKEN EXCHANGE (SWAP) TO WORK.
# 
# HOW TO USE:
# 1. Copy this entire file content
# 2. Replace the placeholder below with your *real* Circle App Kit key
#    (You get this from the Circle Developer dashboard / App Kit section.
#     It usually looks like: KIT_KEY:abc123:secret456...)
# 3. Go to your Vercel project: https://vercel.com/siribraheems-projects/arcpay-web-app
# 4. Settings → Environment Variables
# 5. Click "Import" and paste/upload the content
# 6. IMPORTANT: Select all three targets: Production, Preview, *and* Development
# 7. Save. Then redeploy (or just push a new commit to main — GitHub integration will deploy automatically)
#
# After this, the "Token Exchange" panel in the dashboard will enable the swap button
# and stop showing the configuration warning.
#
# NEVER commit a file containing your real secret to GitHub.

NEXT_PUBLIC_KIT_KEY=your_real_circle_app_kit_key_here

# Optional (if you use Privy social/passkey login)
# NEXT_PUBLIC_PRIVY_APP_ID=your_privy_app_id_here
